org.cleartk.classifier.encoder.features.contextvalue
Class ContextValue

java.lang.Object
  org.cleartk.classifier.encoder.features.contextvalue.ContextValue

public class ContextValue
extends Object


Copyright (c) 2007-2008, Regents of the University of Colorado
All rights reserved.

The name of this class draws from the names of the parameters sent to maxent's MaxentModel.eval method. When we call this method we are going to provide a string array of contexts (roughly feature names) and a corresponding array of values (roughly feature values). We will create these two arrays from objects of type ContextValue which provides a single context/value pair.

Author:
Philip Ogren
See Also:
